{"id":"the-littlest-firefly","slug":"the-littlest-firefly","title":"The Littlest Firefly","title_ko":"가장 작은 반딧불이","level":"A1","ageBand":"8-10","coverUrl":"/seed/the-littlest-firefly/cover.webp","summary_ko":"빛이 약하다고 속상하던 작은 반딧불이가 자기만의 빛을 찾는 밤.","wordCount":118,"pages":[{"id":"the-littlest-firefly-p1","pageNo":1,"spread":"p1","imageUrl":"/seed/the-littlest-firefly/p1.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-littlest-firefly-p1-s1","ord":0,"text":"Pip was the littlest firefly in the woods.","translation_ko":"핍은 숲에서 가장 작은 반딧불이였어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-littlest-firefly/audio/p1-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Pip","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":320},{"word":"was","charStart":4,"charEnd":7,"startMs":320,"endMs":740},{"word":"the","charStart":8,"charEnd":11,"startMs":740,"endMs":1000},{"word":"littlest","charStart":12,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1000,"endMs":1360},{"word":"firefly","charStart":21,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1360,"endMs":2020},{"word":"in","charStart":29,"charEnd":31,"startMs":2020,"endMs":2220},{"word":"the","charStart":32,"charEnd":35,"startMs":2220,"endMs":2660},{"word":"woods","charStart":36,"charEnd":41,"startMs":2660,"endMs":2660}]},{"id":"the-littlest-firefly-p1-s2","ord":1,"text":"His tail had a tiny, soft light.","translation_ko":"핍의 꼬리에는 작고 부드러운 빛이 있었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-littlest-firefly/audio/p1-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"His","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":280},{"word":"tail","charStart":4,"charEnd":8,"startMs":280,"endMs":560},{"word":"had","charStart":9,"charEnd":12,"startMs":560,"endMs":820},{"word":"a","charStart":13,"charEnd":14,"startMs":820,"endMs":1100},{"word":"tiny","charStart":15,"charEnd":19,"startMs":1100,"endMs":1300},{"word":"soft","charStart":21,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1300,"endMs":1680},{"word":"light","charStart":26,"charEnd":31,"startMs":1680,"endMs":1980}]}]},{"id":"the-littlest-firefly-p2","pageNo":2,"spread":"p2","imageUrl":"/seed/the-littlest-firefly/p2.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-littlest-firefly-p2-s1","ord":0,"text":"The big fireflies glowed bright and gold.","translation_ko":"큰 반딧불이들은 환하고 금빛으로 빛났어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-littlest-firefly/audio/p2-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"The","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":260},{"word":"big","charStart":4,"charEnd":7,"startMs":260,"endMs":640},{"word":"fireflies","charStart":8,"charEnd":17,"startMs":640,"endMs":1240},{"word":"glowed","charStart":18,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1240,"endMs":1840},{"word":"bright","charStart":25,"charEnd":31,"startMs":1840,"endMs":2120},{"word":"and","charStart":32,"charEnd":35,"startMs":2120,"endMs":2500},{"word":"gold","charStart":36,"charEnd":40,"startMs":2500,"endMs":2800}]},{"id":"the-littlest-firefly-p2-s2","ord":1,"text":"But Pip's light was very small.","translation_ko":"하지만 핍의 빛은 아주 작았어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-littlest-firefly/audio/p2-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"But","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":340},{"word":"Pip's","charStart":4,"charEnd":9,"startMs":340,"endMs":640},{"word":"light","charStart":10,"charEnd":15,"startMs":640,"endMs":900},{"word":"was","charStart":16,"charEnd":19,"startMs":900,"endMs":1140},{"word":"very","charStart":20,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1140,"endMs":1560},{"word":"small","charStart":25,"charEnd":30,"startMs":1560,"endMs":1820}]}]},{"id":"the-littlest-firefly-p3","pageNo":3,"spread":"p3","imageUrl":"/seed/the-littlest-firefly/p3.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-littlest-firefly-p3-s1","ord":0,"text":"\"My light is too weak,\" Pip said.","translation_ko":"\"내 빛은 너무 약해.\" 핍이 말했어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-littlest-firefly/audio/p3-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"My","charStart":1,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":240},{"word":"light","charStart":4,"charEnd":9,"startMs":240,"endMs":680},{"word":"is","charStart":10,"charEnd":12,"startMs":680,"endMs":1200},{"word":"too","charStart":13,"charEnd":16,"startMs":1200,"endMs":1500},{"word":"weak","charStart":17,"charEnd":21,"startMs":1500,"endMs":2400},{"word":"Pip","charStart":24,"charEnd":27,"startMs":2400,"endMs":2400},{"word":"said","charStart":28,"charEnd":32,"startMs":2400,"endMs":2600}]},{"id":"the-littlest-firefly-p3-s2","ord":1,"text":"He felt sad and flew away alone.","translation_ko":"핍은 슬퍼서 혼자 멀리 날아갔어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-littlest-firefly/audio/p3-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"He","charStart":0,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":280},{"word":"felt","charStart":3,"charEnd":7,"startMs":280,"endMs":560},{"word":"sad","charStart":8,"charEnd":11,"startMs":560,"endMs":1020},{"word":"and","charStart":12,"charEnd":15,"startMs":1020,"endMs":1400},{"word":"flew","charStart":16,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1400,"endMs":1580},{"word":"away","charStart":21,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1580,"endMs":1940},{"word":"alone","charStart":26,"charEnd":31,"startMs":1940,"endMs":2360}]}]},{"id":"the-littlest-firefly-p4","pageNo":4,"spread":"p4","imageUrl":"/seed/the-littlest-firefly/p4.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-littlest-firefly-p4-s1","ord":0,"text":"Then he heard a small voice.","translation_ko":"그때 핍은 작은 목소리를 들었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-littlest-firefly/audio/p4-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Then","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":360},{"word":"he","charStart":5,"charEnd":7,"startMs":360,"endMs":720},{"word":"heard","charStart":8,"charEnd":13,"startMs":720,"endMs":940},{"word":"a","charStart":14,"charEnd":15,"startMs":940,"endMs":1220},{"word":"small","charStart":16,"charEnd":21,"startMs":1220,"endMs":1520},{"word":"voice","charStart":22,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1520,"endMs":1940}]},{"id":"the-littlest-firefly-p4-s2","ord":1,"text":"A little beetle was lost in the dark.","translation_ko":"작은 딱정벌레가 어둠 속에서 길을 잃었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-littlest-firefly/audio/p4-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"A","charStart":0,"charEnd":1,"startMs":0,"endMs":720},{"word":"little","charStart":2,"charEnd":8,"startMs":720,"endMs":940},{"word":"beetle","charStart":9,"charEnd":15,"startMs":940,"endMs":1220},{"word":"was","charStart":16,"charEnd":19,"startMs":1220,"endMs":1560},{"word":"lost","charStart":20,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1560,"endMs":1840},{"word":"in","charStart":25,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1840,"endMs":2120},{"word":"the","charStart":28,"charEnd":31,"startMs":2120,"endMs":2480},{"word":"dark","charStart":32,"charEnd":36,"startMs":2480,"endMs":2500}]}]},{"id":"the-littlest-firefly-p5","pageNo":5,"spread":"p5","imageUrl":"/seed/the-littlest-firefly/p5.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-littlest-firefly-p5-s1","ord":0,"text":"\"I can't find my way home,\" said the beetle.","translation_ko":"\"집에 가는 길을 못 찾겠어.\" 딱정벌레가 말했어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-littlest-firefly/audio/p5-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"I","charStart":1,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":400},{"word":"can't","charStart":3,"charEnd":8,"startMs":400,"endMs":840},{"word":"find","charStart":9,"charEnd":13,"startMs":840,"endMs":1000},{"word":"my","charStart":14,"charEnd":16,"startMs":1000,"endMs":1240},{"word":"way","charStart":17,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1240,"endMs":1460},{"word":"home","charStart":21,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1460,"endMs":2300},{"word":"said","charStart":28,"charEnd":32,"startMs":2300,"endMs":2340},{"word":"the","charStart":33,"charEnd":36,"startMs":2340,"endMs":2500},{"word":"beetle","charStart":37,"charEnd":43,"startMs":2500,"endMs":2680}]}]},{"id":"the-littlest-firefly-p6","pageNo":6,"spread":"p6","imageUrl":"/seed/the-littlest-firefly/p6.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-littlest-firefly-p6-s1","ord":0,"text":"Pip came close to help the beetle.","translation_ko":"핍은 딱정벌레를 도와주려고 가까이 다가갔어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-littlest-firefly/audio/p6-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Pip","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":740},{"word":"came","charStart":4,"charEnd":8,"startMs":740,"endMs":1040},{"word":"close","charStart":9,"charEnd":14,"startMs":1040,"endMs":1400},{"word":"to","charStart":15,"charEnd":17,"startMs":1400,"endMs":1640},{"word":"help","charStart":18,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1640,"endMs":1800},{"word":"the","charStart":23,"charEnd":26,"startMs":1800,"endMs":2000},{"word":"beetle","charStart":27,"charEnd":33,"startMs":2000,"endMs":2180}]},{"id":"the-littlest-firefly-p6-s2","ord":1,"text":"The soft glow showed the small path.","translation_ko":"부드러운 빛이 작은 길을 비춰 주었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-littlest-firefly/audio/p6-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"The","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":420},{"word":"soft","charStart":4,"charEnd":8,"startMs":420,"endMs":760},{"word":"glow","charStart":9,"charEnd":13,"startMs":760,"endMs":1080},{"word":"showed","charStart":14,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1080,"endMs":1420},{"word":"the","charStart":21,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1420,"endMs":1700},{"word":"small","charStart":25,"charEnd":30,"startMs":1700,"endMs":2020},{"word":"path","charStart":31,"charEnd":35,"startMs":2020,"endMs":2400}]}]},{"id":"the-littlest-firefly-p7","pageNo":7,"spread":"p7","imageUrl":"/seed/the-littlest-firefly/p7.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-littlest-firefly-p7-s1","ord":0,"text":"Step by step, they walked home together.","translation_ko":"한 걸음 한 걸음, 둘은 함께 집으로 걸어갔어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-littlest-firefly/audio/p7-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Step","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":400},{"word":"by","charStart":5,"charEnd":7,"startMs":400,"endMs":640},{"word":"step","charStart":8,"charEnd":12,"startMs":640,"endMs":1000},{"word":"they","charStart":14,"charEnd":18,"startMs":1000,"endMs":1700},{"word":"walked","charStart":19,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1700,"endMs":1920},{"word":"home","charStart":26,"charEnd":30,"startMs":1920,"endMs":2260},{"word":"together","charStart":31,"charEnd":39,"startMs":2260,"endMs":2580}]},{"id":"the-littlest-firefly-p7-s2","ord":1,"text":"The beetle smiled and said, \"Thank you!\"","translation_ko":"딱정벌레가 웃으며 말했어요. \"고마워!\"","audioUrl":"/seed/the-littlest-firefly/audio/p7-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"The","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":260},{"word":"beetle","charStart":4,"charEnd":10,"startMs":260,"endMs":560},{"word":"smiled","charStart":11,"charEnd":17,"startMs":560,"endMs":1080},{"word":"and","charStart":18,"charEnd":21,"startMs":1080,"endMs":1400},{"word":"said","charStart":22,"charEnd":26,"startMs":1400,"endMs":1580},{"word":"Thank","charStart":29,"charEnd":34,"startMs":2080,"endMs":2380},{"word":"you","charStart":35,"charEnd":38,"startMs":2380,"endMs":2580}]}]},{"id":"the-littlest-firefly-p8","pageNo":8,"spread":"p8","imageUrl":"/seed/the-littlest-firefly/p8.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-littlest-firefly-p8-s1","ord":0,"text":"Pip looked at his tail again.","translation_ko":"핍은 자기 꼬리를 다시 바라보았어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-littlest-firefly/audio/p8-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Pip","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":360},{"word":"looked","charStart":4,"charEnd":10,"startMs":360,"endMs":800},{"word":"at","charStart":11,"charEnd":13,"startMs":800,"endMs":960},{"word":"his","charStart":14,"charEnd":17,"startMs":960,"endMs":1160},{"word":"tail","charStart":18,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1160,"endMs":1440},{"word":"again","charStart":23,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1440,"endMs":1800}]},{"id":"the-littlest-firefly-p8-s2","ord":1,"text":"His small light was just right.","translation_ko":"핍의 작은 빛은 딱 알맞았어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-littlest-firefly/audio/p8-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"His","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":740},{"word":"small","charStart":4,"charEnd":9,"startMs":740,"endMs":1140},{"word":"light","charStart":10,"charEnd":15,"startMs":1140,"endMs":1440},{"word":"was","charStart":16,"charEnd":19,"startMs":1440,"endMs":1780},{"word":"just","charStart":20,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1780,"endMs":2180},{"word":"right","charStart":25,"charEnd":30,"startMs":2180,"endMs":2460}]}]},{"id":"the-littlest-firefly-p9","pageNo":9,"spread":"p9","imageUrl":"/seed/the-littlest-firefly/p9.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-littlest-firefly-p9-s1","ord":0,"text":"Now Pip glows happily every night.","translation_ko":"이제 핍은 밤마다 행복하게 빛나요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-littlest-firefly/audio/p9-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Now","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":1080},{"word":"Pip","charStart":4,"charEnd":7,"startMs":1080,"endMs":1340},{"word":"glows","charStart":8,"charEnd":13,"startMs":1340,"endMs":1800},{"word":"happily","charStart":14,"charEnd":21,"startMs":1800,"endMs":2180},{"word":"every","charStart":22,"charEnd":27,"startMs":2180,"endMs":2660},{"word":"night","charStart":28,"charEnd":33,"startMs":2660,"endMs":2880}]},{"id":"the-littlest-firefly-p9-s2","ord":1,"text":"Every light is special, big or small.","translation_ko":"크든 작든, 모든 빛은 특별해요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-littlest-firefly/audio/p9-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Every","charStart":0,"charEnd":5,"startMs":0,"endMs":860},{"word":"light","charStart":6,"charEnd":11,"startMs":860,"endMs":1160},{"word":"is","charStart":12,"charEnd":14,"startMs":1160,"endMs":1420},{"word":"special","charStart":15,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1420,"endMs":1800},{"word":"big","charStart":24,"charEnd":27,"startMs":2520,"endMs":2600},{"word":"or","charStart":28,"charEnd":30,"startMs":2600,"endMs":3020},{"word":"small","charStart":31,"charEnd":36,"startMs":3020,"endMs":3300}]}]}],"quiz":[{"question_ko":"핍은 어떤 반딧불이였나요?","type":"mc","options":["숲에서 가장 큰 반딧불이","숲에서 가장 작은 반딧불이","가장 빠른 반딧불이","가장 나이 많은 반딧불이"],"answerIndex":1,"explain_ko":"핍은 숲에서 가장 작은 반딧불이였어요.","id":"the-littlest-firefly-q1","ord":0},{"question_ko":"핍은 처음에 자기 빛에 대해 어떻게 느꼈나요?","type":"mc","options":["빛이 약해서 속상했어요","빛이 밝아서 자랑스러웠어요","빛에 관심이 없었어요","빛이 무서웠어요"],"answerIndex":0,"explain_ko":"핍은 자기 빛이 너무 약하다고 생각해서 슬펐어요.","id":"the-littlest-firefly-q2","ord":1},{"question_ko":"핍이 어둠 속에서 만난 것은 누구였나요?","type":"mc","options":["길 잃은 딱정벌레","큰 반딧불이","잠든 새","다른 반딧불이 친구"],"answerIndex":0,"explain_ko":"핍은 길을 잃은 작은 딱정벌레를 만났어요.","id":"the-littlest-firefly-q3","ord":2},{"question_ko":"핍은 딱정벌레를 어떻게 도와주었나요?","type":"mc","options":["큰 소리로 불렀어요","빛으로 길을 비춰 주었어요","집을 지어 주었어요","먹이를 나눠 주었어요"],"answerIndex":1,"explain_ko":"핍의 부드러운 빛이 길을 비춰 딱정벌레를 집으로 데려다주었어요.","id":"the-littlest-firefly-q4","ord":3},{"question_ko":"이 이야기가 알려 주는 것은 무엇인가요?","type":"mc","options":["빛은 클수록 좋아요","크든 작든 모든 빛은 특별해요","혼자 있는 것이 좋아요","밤은 무서운 시간이에요"],"answerIndex":1,"explain_ko":"작은 빛도 누군가를 도울 수 있고, 모든 빛은 저마다 특별해요.","id":"the-littlest-firefly-q5","ord":4}]}